9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4</a><br />\n泛民，要學馬丁路德金。<br />\n我不反對不支持勇武，但理解。請在勇武前冷靜想清楚後果(自己和旁人）.不受傷，不流血。<br />\n「我有一個夢」背後有「選票與子彈」支持同保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=45a82cf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈</a>"},{"pid":"2b3832b91a548aa5aa0e61d327007c6942176571","tid":1313842,"uid":48061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"Blocked"},{"pid":"96fcdae8ff4a1e9ae5e1651f4e9b19dfb5c93045","tid":1313842,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:04:37.000Z","msg":"2萬5都冇人去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ad55c755838fcb19df0e526d6064d0691c8ac5","tid":1313842,"uid":274667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"乜撚野年代，成撚日講親耳 但錄音影張相都無?<br />\n收皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"66d2f9667744449e268c257a4a0bb4d3c1e84474","tid":1313842,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"攪咪攪囉，反正黑警自己都會攪啦"},{"pid":"2bb36f46e2a15725249a5b7b9b99958d1dbdc602","tid":1313842,"uid":28849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}